cuSolverDN : Dense Linear Algebra Library

Cholesky factorization and its solverLU FactorizationRow pivotingLU solveQR factorizationgenerate unitary matrix Q from QR factorizationcompute Q**T*b in solve min||A*x = b||L*D*L**T,U*D*U**T factorizationbidiagonal factorizationgenerates one of the unitary matrices Q or P**T determined by GEBRDtridiagonal factorizationgenerate unitary Q comes from sytrdcompute op(Q)*C or C*op(Q) where Q comes from sytrdsingular value decomposition, A = U * Sigma * V^Hstandard symmetric eigenvalue solver, A*x = lambda*x, by divide-and-conquergeneralized symmetric eigenvalue solver, A*x = lambda*B*x, by divide-and-conquer
